{"tid":2093493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要移民嘅手足入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-07-04T01:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T17:06:14.000Z","uid":67553,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7438cecc7197a629a329e1af9758bbe14b7458f6","tid":2093493,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:17:04.000Z","msg":"我哋成日睇猶太人、波蘭人經歷眾多苦難，但係佢哋究竟點解過咗幾代都仲記得自己本身嘅身份？就係文化&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋唔知香港人未來會面對啲咩，但係如果選擇去其他地方生活又可以做啲咩？就係盡快搵身邊嘅朋友成立<span style=\"color: red;\">香港會</span>、長遠要建立<span style=\"color: red;\">香港國際學校</span>，等全世界都知咩叫<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人──熱愛民主自由、溫文有禮、有智慧、勇敢嘅人</span>。只有咁樣，我哋香港人嘅文化習俗先可以得以保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果真的去到外國，首先梗係要盡快融入人哋社會，學人哋嘅語言、文化</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後當然要同身邊嘅香港朋友多啲聚會啦！去大家屋企煮下<strong>家鄉餸菜</strong>，<strong>新年、中秋、冬至、聖誕、復活節</strong>呢啲喺香港會做嘅事，全部都要繼續做！再慢慢做大個餅，認識同一個國家/城市嘅其他香港人，我哋生咗下一代亦都要等佢哋加入呢個圈子，同埋一定要學廣東話。<br />\n<br />\n一步一步做落去，我相信一定可以保留到我哋香港嘅文化同歷史！就算之後再有手足想過嚟，即刻就知可以搵咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51b7197a38ad99a9d159f17c4a4cbf91d789396","tid":2093493,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495e680b32e5d186540dd66ff2e7699d2d63ca19","tid":2093493,"uid":67553,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"樓主好𠹌睿智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a4fa9ee603c9fbbd8f3b767ab4fe475876705b","tid":2093493,"uid":15010,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:20:15.000Z","msg":"成立海外組織<br />\n幫海外港人係名自所屬國家落地生根<br />\n同時同海外會交流，維繫散落世界各地既香港人<br />\n定期聚會、用廣東話、傳承文化<br />\n俾香港人同後代每個星期最少一次可以用廣東話<br />\n<br />\n最重要係課金、建立銀彈網絡<br />\n爭取社會上、甚至係國際上既話語權<br />\n<br />\n最後一定要嚴格審查入會既人<br />\n有新人加入要最少10個會員endorse<br />\n提防狗隻共諜滲入"},{"pid":"01b09108a1b9d67a05bf60f4a007757beb4b4c40","tid":2093493,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73dfb20d60facd71feb76af5a406398bc2a78de","tid":2093493,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6a78328451e6e7d62e83d150115e3df327097a","tid":2093493,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港會"},{"pid":"5ba1b020c15455c5b55adb5af479a312505c7b0c","tid":2093493,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1326a51a76d1d48ed767d51db23cf01f9694b744","tid":2093493,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb50cdbab8da9b5089d57d9a1083cf04c982d2f7","tid":2093493,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e809497003292bceb90441af2e70e1c986b31066","tid":2093493,"uid":36014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:35:07.000Z","msg":"國際學校呢個真係要做<br />\n但要好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73daac1107ad66aff16ae0e2b4bbf027a95331fa","tid":2093493,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\